  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA4">
<l>nakariḻaittu nittilattu nāṇmalarkoṇ ṭāṅkē</l>
<l>tikaḻu maṇivayirañ cērttu – nikarillāp</l>
<l>paiṅkamala mēntip paṇintēṉ paṉimalarā</l>
<l>ḷaṅkamvalaṅ koṇṭā ṉaṭi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Building a temple, taking day[-fresh] blossoms with [dew] pearls, there</l>
<l>combining [them] with glittering sapphires [and] diamonds,</l>
<l>offering incomparable fresh lotus I humbled myself before the feet of him</l>
<l>who took her from the dewy [lotus] blossom onto the right of [his] body.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
